<a href="http://www.jensenestatelaw.com/" class="pathway">Home</a> <img src="/images/M_images/arrow.png" alt=""  /> <a href="/colleagues" class="pathway">Colleagues</a> <img src="/images/M_images/arrow.png" alt=""  /> <a href="/colleagues/newsletters" class="pathway">Wealth Counselor</a> <img src="/images/M_images/arrow.png" alt=""  /> Planning for the New &quot;Zero Percent&quot; Tax Bracket</span>

